Class RequestGuardFactoryGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.endpoint.RequestGuardFactoryGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Field

    public class RequestGuardFactoryGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
implements Field
    Java source code generator for generating usages of RequestGuardFactory instances. This generator represents request guard factories that are stored as fields.
